      "value": "<p><strong>Dream Stealer (Fetish)</strong></p><p><em>Creation Cost: 5 Gnosis.</em></p><p><strong>Effect:</strong></p><p>While within 10 feet of a sleeping creature:</p><ul><li>You may view its dreams for up to 10 minutes</li><li>You gain advantage on Charisma checks made to interact with that creature for 24 hours</li><li>The target does not know their dreams were observed.</li></ul><p><strong>Fetish Rating:</strong> 2. <strong>Minimum Max Gnosis:</strong> 5. Cannot use while raging unless this fetish states otherwise. Spirit Attention: you can have a number of actively empowered fetishes equal to your Wisdom modifier (minimum 1); instantaneous effects do not count after resolution.</p><p><code>[GAROU_FETISH] id=dream-stealer; rating=2; minGnosis=5; activation=action</code></p>",
      "chat": "<p>Fetish (Rating 2). Min Max Gnosis 5. Within 10 ft of a sleeping creature: view its dreams up to 10 min; advantage on Cha checks vs that creature for 24 hours; target does not know.</p>"
